g.ns136:text: \\begin{align*}\n\\varepsilon_1 =& \\dfrac{\\partial u_r}{\\partial r} + \\frac{u_r}{r} +\\frac{\\partial u_z}{\\partial z} \\\\\n\\varepsilon_2 =& u_r \\dfrac{\\partial u_r}{\\partial r} + u_z\\dfrac{\\partial u_r}{\\partial z} + \\dfrac{\\partial p}{\\partial r} \\\\\n&- \\left(\\dfrac{1}{Re} + \\nu_T^{*}\\right) \\left[\\dfrac{\\partial^2u_r}{\\partial r^2} + \\dfrac{1}{r}\\dfrac{\\partial u_r}{\\partial r} + \\dfrac{\\partial^2 u_r}{\\partial z^{2}} - \\dfrac{u_r}{r^{2}}\\right]\\\\\n\\varepsilon_3 =& u_r \\dfrac{\\partial u_z}{\\partial r} + u_z \\dfrac{\\partial u_z}{\\partial z} + \\dfrac{\\partial p}{\\partial z}\\\\\n&- \\left(\\dfrac{1}{Re} + \\nu_T^{*}\\right) \\left[\\dfrac{\\partial^2u_z}{\\partial r^2} + \\dfrac{1}{r}\\dfrac{\\partial u_z}{\\partial r} + \\dfrac{\\partial^2 u_z}{\\partial z^{2}}\\right]\n\\end{align*}
